The paper discusses an approach for model evolution in UML model libraries, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of graphs and quality models, which are related to programming languages (cs.PL) and machine learning (cs.LG). The proactive guidance and review mechanism mentioned in the paper are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the need for model repositories, which can be related to databases (cs.DB).
